{"word":"G460 - ἀνόμως - anómōs - an-om'-oce - Without law","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀνόμως</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">anómōs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-om'-oce</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Without law</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"நியாயப்பிரமாணம் இல்லாமல் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"without the law"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Adverb from <a href=\"#/G459 - ἄνομος - ánomos - an'-om-os/459\">G459</a>; <i>lawlessly</i>, that is, (specifically) <i>not amenable to</i> (the Jewish) <i>law:</i> - without law.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1772/1772\">G1772</a>, <a href=\"#/G3544/3544\">G3544</a>, <a href=\"#/G3545/3545\">G3545</a>, <a href=\"#/G3547/3547\">G3547</a>, <a href=\"#/G3548/3548\">G3548</a>, <a href=\"#/G3549/3549\">G3549</a>, <a href=\"#/G3550/3550\">G3550</a>, <a href=\"#/G3551/3551\">G3551</a>, <a href=\"#/G3891/3891\">G3891</a>, <a href=\"#/G3892/3892\">G3892</a>, <a href=\"#/G458/458\">G458</a>, <a href=\"#/G459/459\">G459</a>, <a href=\"#/G460/460\">G460</a>"}]}